title: Oralloy Core Preset
description: You spent years meditating upon salt and radio waves. By divine providence, you happened upon a tin containing a high-grade metal pill. Consuming it has brought your latent potential to the surface. Pilgrimage is necessary to realize it. This is an unstable genome chimera preset with high toughness and the nomad calling. Created for the October 2024 Pets and Presets modjam.
author: Monosophy
